#: ../../source/vuln/sql/privilege.rst:2
msgid "权限提升"
msgstr "Privilege Escalation"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/privilege.rst:5
msgid "UDF提权"
msgstr "UDF Privilege Escalation"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/privilege.rst:6
msgid ""
"UDF（User Defined "
"Function，用户自定义函数）是MySQL提供的一个功能，可以通过编写DLL扩展为MySQL添加新函数，扩充其功能。"
msgstr ""
"UDF (User Defined Function) is a MySQL feature that allows new functions to "
"be added to MySQL by writing DLL extensions."

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/privilege.rst:8
msgid "当获得MySQL权限之后，即可通过这种方式上传自定义的扩展文件，从MySQL中执行系统命令。"
msgstr "After obtaining MySQL privileges, an attacker can use this method to upload a custom extension file and execute system commands from MySQL."
